{
  "name": "Taijutsu Expertise",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-orange.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Taijutsu </p><p>Your Focus in the heat of Combat and mastery of the martial arts, allow you to fight with much greater efficiency.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• Select one between Taijutsu or Bukijutsu.</p><p> You may use Dexterity instead of Strength as your Taijutsu Modifier when casting the chosen jutsu type.</p><p>• You may use Dexterity instead of Strength for your Unarmed Attack and damage rolls.</p><p>• You may use Dexterity when making a Martial Arts Checks.</p><p>• You may take this feat again, select the jutsu type you didn't select the first time.</p><p></p>",
